[3] Cholera - India (Kerala)
Date: Fri 24 Jun 2011
Source: AsiaNetIndia [edited]
http://www.asianetindia.com/news/man-dies-cholera-kapetta_280284.html


A 32 year old man has died of cholera at Kalpetta in Wayanad district
on Friday [24 Jun 2011]. The deceased has been identified as a
resident of Paniya adivasi colony. This is the 1st cholera death that
has been reported in the past 5 years in the state.

